      <li><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman","serif";font-size:16px;'>k&ouml;rnyezetbar&aacute;t, &eacute;s az alkalmazott koncentr&aacute;ci&oacute;ban az emberre&nbsp;vesz&eacute;lytelen.</span></li>
